      "writtenOn": "2026-05-19T06:39:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I understand the intent to support both paths coexisting, but I don\u0027t think flipping the default to enabled is the right approach here.\n\nChanging the default silently activates inotify for all builds that don\u0027t explicitly set the option — consumers pick up a behavioral change without opting into it. That\u0027s especially problematic for platforms that lack the watched directory or that relied on the D-Bus-only path.\n\nI\u0027d suggest leaving the default as disabled and letting callers opt in explicitly. That keeps it a conscious per-platform decision rather than something imposed on everyone.",
      "revId": "2eed770eaf5e38a5ac36a9e7239c2745f461ec33",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    }
